{"tid":366821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"pc router用家揮手區","createTime":"2017-08-20T10:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:11:58.000Z","uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0fdb8ee2854dd7dd0823d17ff9aaeddc8f71b8f","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"超高nat性能，絕不輕機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a10602917d0a5058b6dc9890b31bff79b826c37","tid":366821,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"想知你成套setup 係點"},{"pid":"b1444420567561a1e1816d2fc40aee421e097384","tid":366821,"uid":115503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"用緊pfsense路過，用左一年都係好穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad89627454497b2fe8bfc642b1b2c00d383edf4c","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知你成套setup 係點</blockquote><br />\nmodem-&gt;pc router-&gt;r8000<br />\n<br />\npc係一部deskmini 110既barebone黎，體積好細，cpu用i7 7700，ram有32gb，ssd用兩隻750gb行raid 1<br />\n<br />\n網絡硬件方面，modem果條線插主機板，有兩隻orico既usb lan卡+usb 1開3，類似呢款<br />\n<img src=\"http://orico.cc/images/201508/goods_img/4780_P_1440005970832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forico.cc%2Fimages%2F201508%2Fgoods_img%2F4780_P_1440005970832.jpg&h=78d8f730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有一隻lan卡A插底板usb 3，lan port穿牆房果部電腦，另一張lan卡B就插lan卡A既usb，lan port插r8000<br />\n<br />\n軟件方面，pc router用arch linux，跟網上教學輕易就整到router功能，r8000就刷左ddwrt<br />\n<br />\nnat性能方面，同房果部機通信iperf3單向有940mbps，雙向有1900mbps<br />\n<br />\n最近考慮緊買個200蚊既wifi卡，令部pc router放埋wifi，將部r8000搬去第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd111951ebb8e6645a0a5a2a51509607d34a4606","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"當然，唔想煩/學野，最好買d專用既x86電腦(4個lan port+wifi)，用pfsense啦"},{"pid":"502446223e0db14db701aaa01338ae28d62e1ba5","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"上面果款usb lan金的士有得買"},{"pid":"d59d959da988f4d9f101b3c1f11bc67c97be5e4d","tid":366821,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"router冇6核點開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e049c3f492d066e79f446dabb74fb84f6c02e4a","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>router冇6核點開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nrouter唔洗咁勁，desktop先要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c96c193cf4974a976c69d633e9f4d180226b005","tid":366821,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"點解pc router 要用到i7 同埋750gb ssd<br />\n當nas 用?"},{"pid":"e2afcece1726d54c4a6671d75085f86fa1d9419a","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解pc router 要用到i7 同埋750gb ssd<br />\n當nas 用?</blockquote><br />\n本來用黎做minecraft server，但個plan廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家部機都有好多用途，gitlab aria2 shadowsocks nginx php node dnscrypt emby kodi樣樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n部機駁落廳部電視，實際上都係htpc黎，可以用kodi播戲，用手機command部電視播youtube，moonlight-embedded + xbox 無線手掣將房果部電腦畫面stream落電視打機完全冇問題<br />\n<br />\n插個usb3 2bay 4bay做返nas都得，甚至m2轉返pcie插張1070，行gpu passthrough裝windows打機/vr都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n超多用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9490d3a89377500beea41487b8519bc377e22527","tid":366821,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T22:58:14.000Z","msg":"如果用arch linux 再搭張4 port intel lan 卡<br />\n係咪可以做埋load balance 唔使用pfsense"},{"pid":"92d06fc34b1c8fdaa23468557b77d52aab1c4840","tid":366821,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果用arch linux 再搭張4 port intel lan 卡<br />\n係咪可以做埋load balance 唔使用pfsense</blockquote><br />\nload balance未知點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b7a3bddfe6ee37249568caf036fa7a5ab0b0b6","tid":366821,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果用arch linux 再搭張4 port intel lan 卡<br />\n係咪可以做埋load balance 唔使用pfsense</blockquote><br />\nload balance未知點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIT 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢架喎"},{"pid":"6f2c4347c08691e106a323e525ae9167bda77517","tid":366821,"uid":67054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果用arch linux 再搭張4 port intel lan 卡<br />\n係咪可以做埋load balance 唔使用pfsense</blockquote><br />\nload balance未知點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIT 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢架喎</blockquote><br />\n用F5 啦 如果玩load balance <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd51fa4546a512b8db3e0dd635302466761db8ca","tid":366821,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解pc router 要用到i7 同埋750gb ssd<br />\n當nas 用?</blockquote><br />\n本來用黎做minecraft server，但個plan廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家部機都有好多用途，gitlab aria2 shadowsocks nginx php node dnscrypt emby kodi樣樣做<img src=\"/assets/fac